PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the PELICAN LAKE BAND, of certain land in Saskatchewan, mines and minerals included, as follows: (a) 127 hectares as an addition to Pelican Lake Indian Reserve No. 191-A, and (b) another 48 hectares as an addition to its Reserve No. 191-B.
